reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Multi use cubes for just about it all
reviews.reviewText: Although these run just a bit smaller than I'd like, I was able to make them work for various items. Love that this set comes with bags as well. The mesh makes it easy to see what is inside for quick retrieval. Makes packing a bit easier.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Plenty of various sizes to keep luggage organized
reviews.reviewText: This pack has a great variety of sizes for use in different travel bags. Like the black color, which should not show any dirt with prolonged use. The zipper has nice hooped pulls but is thin nylon that stuck occasionally especially when the bag was not loaded. The zipper opens three full sides for easy packing and I like the tie-down straps in the bigger bags. They are thin materials that compress to help with packing. The mesh top allows you to see what is packed in the bag.
